(1 row)
</programlisting>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   以下是使用两种不同的实际数据类型作为参数的输出：

<programlisting>
SELECT attrelid::regclass, array_accum(attname)
    FROM pg_attribute
    WHERE attnum &gt; 0 AND attrelid = 'pg_tablespace'::regclass
